lead_paragraph: Clemson's Dabo Swinney and Virginia Tech's Justin Fuente will be on opposite sidelines in Saturday's ACC Championship game, but they were almost much closer than that.

headline.print_headline: ACC Championship: Opposing Coaches Almost Worked Together
